title.rendered: Ultra Luxurious Apartment For Sale In Westend

content.rendered:
With a total plot area of 500 sq yds and a Built-up area of 2700 sqft, this super luxury floor has 4 bedrooms with attached bathrooms, a guest toilet that has Italian marble cladding with high-end sanitary ware, and excellent fittings. It has an automatic doors Schindler lift that can easily accommodate up to 6 passengers. The puja room faces the northeast side. The high-end modular kitchen on this floor has a jaw-drop finish of wooden work, modern design, separate access door to the spacious balcony. With this floor, you get 3 car parking spaces in the stilt with exclusive gates plus a separate reception area as well.
☀️High-End Construction
☀️Premium Location
☀️Rear Park with 2 bedrooms facing greenery
☀️Club With Swimming Pool
☀️Secured Neighborhood
☀️Separate Reception Area
☀️Perfect Vastu
☀️North-East Facing
☀️4 Bedrooms With Attached Bathrooms
☀️3 Car Parking With Separate Gates
☀️Schindler Lift With Automatic Doors
☀️Wrap Around Balcony in front & on sides
☀️Modular Kitchen
☀️Spacious Balcony
West End Colony is a prestigious address, which is home to many influential, affluent, Super rich & businessmen.
This is just 10 minutes away from airports, Embassies, Foreign Missions, High Commissions, American schools, and British schools. ITC Maurya Sheraton, Taj Palace is just a minute’s drive. It has a club with a small gym and a swimming pool. Its RWA is very well managed and organized.
📞 Call On 9818312077 For Site Visit
Follow @royalerealtorsindia on social media
